<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>
    RailEase ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy. 
    This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our app.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Personal Information:</b> We may collect your name when you post in the Q&A section. This name will be displayed publicly along with your questions and comments.</li>
    <li><b>User-Generated Content:</b> Any questions or comments you post in the Q&A section are visible to other users.</li>
    <li><b>Non-Personal Information:</b> We may collect basic usage data (such as device type, app version, and usage patterns) to improve app performance.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
  <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Allow users to post questions and comments with their chosen name.</li>
    <li>Provide and improve app services (PNR status, station layout, train times, chart vacancy, retiring room booking, help & support).</li>
    <li>Enhance app performance and fix technical issues.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Visibility</h2>
  <p>
    Your name and any content you post in the Q&A section are visible to all users of the app. 
    Please avoid sharing sensitive personal information.
  </p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    RailEase may use third-party services such as Google Play Services, which have their own privacy policies. 
    We encourage you to review their policies for more details.
  </p>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell or share your personal information (such as your name) with third parties. 
    However, any user-generated content you post is publicly visible within the app.
  </p>

  <h2>User Responsibilities</h2>
  <p>
    Users are responsible for the content they post in the Q&A section. 
    Please ensure your name and comments are appropriate and respectful.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: 
    <a href="mailto:thekonkanstudios@gmail.com">thekonkanstudios@gmail.com</a>
  </p>
</body>
